# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# Create a Web Application Client ID from Google Cloud Console:
# https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#
# For local development:
# 1. Add "http://localhost:3000" to "Authorized JavaScript origins"
#
# For Vercel/Cloudflare deployment:
# 1. Create a separate Client ID (or reuse with additional origins)
# 2. Add your deploy URL (e.g., "https://your-app.vercel.app") to origins
# 3. Set this environment variable in your hosting platform's dashboard
#
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_CLIENT_ID_HERE
